  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <head>Cēṉāvaraiyar</head>
        <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Ci. Vai. Tamōtarampiḷḷai</persName> 1868, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n73/mode/1up">70</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n73/mode/1up">70</ref>.</p>
      <p>eḻuvāyvēṟṟumaiyuṇartti ēṉaiyaṟuvakai vēṟṟumaiyilakkaṇamumuṇarttiya veṭuttukkoṇṭār.</p>
<p>i - ḷ. peyar, ai, oṭu, ku, iṉ, atu, kaṇ eṉṟu kūṟappaṭṭa muṟaimaiyaiyuṭaiya urupu tannilai tiriyātu peyark kīṟāmiyalpaiyuṭaiyaveṉṟu colluvar āciriyar. e - ṟu.</p>
<p>u - m. cāttaṉai, cāttaṉoṭu, cāttaṟku, cāttaṉiṉ, cāttaṉatu, cāttaṉkaṇ eṉa varum.</p>
<p>avai yeṇṇuppeyarāṉ vaḻaṅkappaṭutaliṟ kūṟiya muṟaiyiṉurupeṉṟār.</p>
<p>viṉaiccoliṟuti niṟkumiṭaiccoṟṟāmeṉa vēṟuṇarappaṭātu accoṟkuṟuppāy niṟkumaṉṟē, ivai yavvāṟu peyark kuṟuppākātu tāmeṉa vēṟuṇarappaṭṭiṟuti niṟkumeṉpār nilaitiriyāteṉṟār.</p>
<p>urupu peyarcārntu varumeṉavē, urupēṟṟalākiya peyarilakkaṇamum peṟappaṭṭatu.	(8)</p>
    </body>
  </text>
